4. That he has talked of the Plot with Kane and Kelly often, and has been at Kane's Houſe, and has heard that other Soldiers were concerned, but does not know them. That he has ſeen Quack (Walter's) there, Ryndert's Tom, Governour's Jack, Cuyler's Pedro;

